{"tid":768315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now新聞台】調查指「麥難民」人數增三成","createTime":"2018-08-05T09:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T11:14:40.000Z","uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9a8dc673cdfcf6fb757a947bbb5ba804cc7de1","tid":768315,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Z1MBjRkkTwa43azjFbBE5A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/HOMELESS.PC.1600.0508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZ1MBjRkkTwa43azjFbBE5A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FHOMELESS.PC.1600.0508.jpg&h=f06079ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有團體調查發現，在快餐店麥當勞夜宿的人，即俗稱的「麥難民」人數有上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n太平山青年商會在六月巡察麥當勞116間分店，統計有334人在店內夜宿，較2015年多三成，而接受訪問的53人中，一半年齡45至64歲，而25歲或以下的比例由去年不足百分之一急增至近百分之六，當中年紀最小只有19歲。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，七成受訪者有固定居所，包括公屋或劏房等，他們為節省電費或追求舒適及安全感等而選擇在快餐店夜宿。"},{"pid":"76104713754734680b40ceb687558c5c3f1fbef8","tid":768315,"uid":5389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:30:42.000Z","msg":"起碼有冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a456d940d34190866b6bf7b5b751ffc733db53b","tid":768315,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"追求舒適及安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b845a5d0c2c0cfbb9405e54d562b99eacdc36672","tid":768315,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>追求舒適及安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為快餐店分別有閉路電視及當值員工，<br />\n即使有事都可以迅速應對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" 